replies.body:
I've actually been having the same issue as well.

I'm on the NA server and just a week or so ago my ping was always around 40. But specifically after this patch it has jumped to 120 and doesn't fluctuate much from that. I checked my router and everything seems fine. Any other game I play has no issues with the ping being high (Still sticks to 40 ping and doesnt get much higher). I've tried everything from shutting down every other program  that uses internet to completely un-installing league and doing a fresh install/update but the issue has persisted (Though the fresh install did make the client run more smoothly for me so there's that)

{{champion:27}}
